projects.description:
On various occasions, RWS asks for technological advice concerning field measurements. This has led to:
* an inventory on wave-ADCP’s (ADCP = Acoustic Doppler Current Profiler) (compiled in 2011);
* an inquiry into the performance of Interocean S4 PUV-sensors as applied in the Petten measurement site during storms (compiled in 2012); 
* an explanation for observed spurious differences in low-frequency wave energy offshore the Dutch Zeeland estuary (compiled in 2013);
* an explanation for the observed differences in wave parameters measured at the same locations (compiled in 2014);
* an explanation for the observed differences in water levels measured from measurement poles at the same locations (compiled in 2014 and 2015).
